</p>
<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyQYWjX8ufw" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Watch on YouTube</a></figure>
<p>"Your love and support keeps us going and we can't wait to show you our fourth game," <a href="https://x.com/HazelightGames/status/2041820156607742336">Hazelight said on X.</a> <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/hazelight-next-new-game-in-development">The studio announced that it was working a new game earlier this year</a>, and though we know nothing yet about it, I expect it will feature co-op heavily.</p>

